<div class = 'app-card-container'>
    
    <div class = 'card'>
        <h1>About Me </h1>

        <hr>

        <div class = 'row'>
            <div class = 'col-md-5'>
                <%= image_tag "profile_image.JPG", width: '100%', alt: 'profile image', class: 'profile-image' %>

                <div class ='skils'>
                    <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                        <div class = 'skill'>
                            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                            <div class='progress'>
                                <div 
                                    class='progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning'
                                    role='progressbar'
                                    aria-valuenow='<%= skill.percent_utilized %> ' 
                                    aria-valuemax='100'
                                    style='width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%' 
                                >
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class = 'col-md-7'>
                <p>I have spent just under half a decade ensuring the quality of software put in front of the users' faces.
                Ive recently decided to take that knowledge of what makes a good software product and shift my focus to helping
                build out those qualities.</p>

                <p>The ideal situation for me is coming into a high energy group that is passionate about what they do but also knows
                how to have a good time outside of work. An environment full of empathy where I'm able to learn and be mentored from 
                engineers who are as willing and excited to teach me as I am to learn from them. </p>

                <p> 
                    <button
                        class = 'btn btn-outline-warning'
                        type = 'button'
                        data-toggle='collapse'
                        data-target='#jobHistory'
                        aria-expanded='false'
                        aria-controller='jobHistory'
                    >
                    Job History 
                    </button>

                    <button
                        class = 'btn btn-outline-warning'
                        type = 'button'
                        data-toggle='collapse'
                        data-target='#education'
                        aria-expanded='false'
                        aria-controller='education'
                    >
                    Education 
                    </button>

                </p>

                <p>
                    <div class = 'collapse' id='jobHistory'>
                        <div class = 'card card-block bg-warning'>
                            <Span class = 'job-title'>QA Engineer</Span>
                            <Span class = 'job-company'>SimpleNexus</Span>
                            <Span class = 'job-date'>Oct. 2020 - Current</Span>
                        </div>
                        <div class = 'card card-block bg-warning'>
                            <Span class = 'job-title'>QA Team Lead</Span>
                            <Span class = 'job-company'>Alsco</Span>
                            <Span class = 'job-date'>Aug. 2019 - May 2020</Span>
                        </div>
                        <div class = 'card card-block bg-warning'>
                            <Span class = 'job-title'>QA Engineer</Span>
                            <Span class = 'job-company'>eFileCabinet</Span>
                            <Span class = 'job-date'>Jun. 2016 - Jun.2017, Jan. 2018 - Aug. 2019</Span>
                        </div>
                        
                    </div>

                    <div class = 'collapse' id='education'>
                        <div class = 'card card-block bg-warning'>
                            <span class = 'job-title'>Associates</span>
                            <span class = 'job-company'>Computer Science: Information Systems</span>
                            <span class = 'job-date'>Salt Lake Community College</span>
                        </div>
                         <div class = 'card card-block bg-warning'>
                            <span class = 'job-title'>Certificate</span>
                            <span class = 'job-company'>Full Stack Web Development</span>
                            <span class = 'job-date'>DevPointLabs</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class = 'resume-button'>
                            <%= link_to 'Full Resume', '2021_resume.pdf', download: '', class:"btn btn-warning"  %> 
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


